Buriat and khk

                            apertium-bua-khk
===============================================================================

This is an Apertium language pair for translating between Buriat and 
khk. What you can use this language package for:

* Translating between Buriat and khk
* Morphological analysis of Buriat and khk
* Part-of-speech tagging of Buriat and khk

For information on the latter two points, see subheading "For more 
information" below

Requirements
===============================================================================

You will need the following software installed:

* lttoolbox (>= 3.3.0)
* apertium (>= 3.3.0)
* vislcg3 (>= 0.9.9.10297)


If this does not make any sense, we recommend you look at: www.apertium.org

Compiling
===============================================================================

Given the requirements being installed, you should be able to just run:

$ ./configure 
$ make
# make install

You can use ./autogen.sh instead of ./configure you're compiling from
SVN. If you installed any prerequisite language packages using a --prefix
to ./configure, make sure to give the same --prefix to ./configure here.

Testing
===============================================================================

If you are in the source directory after running make, the following
commands should work:

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium -d . bua-khk
TODO test translated sentence 1

$ echo "TODO test sentence 2" | apertium -d . khk-bua
TODO test translated sentence 2

After installing somewhere in $PATH, you should be able to do e.g.

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium bua-khk
TODO test translated sentence 1

Files and data
===============================================================================

* apertium-bua-khk.bua-khk.dix  - Bilingual dictionary
* apertium-bua-khk.bua-khk.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into Buriat
* apertium-bua-khk.khk-bua.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into khk
* apertium-bua-khk.bua-khk.t2x  - Chunking rules for translating into Buriat
* apertium-bua-khk.khk-bua.t2x  - Chunking rules for translating into khk
* apertium-bua-khk.bua-khk.t3x  - Chunking rules for translating into Buriat
* apertium-bua-khk.khk-bua.t3x  - Chunking rules for translating into khk
* apertium-bua-khk.bua-khk.rlx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into Buriat
* apertium-bua-khk.khk-bua.rlx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into khk
* modes.xml                     - Translation modes

For more information
